Usage: {TPIL, TPIV, TPIT} [OPTION]...

  -d DIRECTORY  load DIRECTORY on startup
  -e EXPRESSION use EXPRESSION as search expression
  -M SIZE       use SIZE as maximum file size
  -m SIZE       use SIZE as minimum file size
  -s            perform a search
  -D            perform a dump
  -o FILENAME   copy search session log to FILENAME
  -h            display this help message and exit
  -b            batch mode (don't run console after processing flags)

  For usage of the interactive command line, use the 'help' command or refer to
the supplied documentation.
